Global Buclizine Market Insights
Buclizine Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Buclizine Market Overview
The Buclizine market is estimated to experience steady growth, driven by its significant demand in treating motion sickness, nausea, and as an appetite stimulant. The global market value of Buclizine is expected to reach USD 300 million by 2030, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6% from 2025. Buclizine is primarily used in the pharmaceutical industry, particularly in the form of tablets, capsules, and syrups, with an expanding application in both adult and pediatric populations. The growing healthcare sector and increased awareness regarding motion sickness and nausea treatments contribute to the rising market value.

